{"tid":1344739,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"柳俊江因爲有良知先離開TVB","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T14:37:17.000Z","uid":38451,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b59633274016a9e28ee047d8b9e9b5cb7d4ca7e6","tid":1344739,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者工作</span><br />\n柳俊江於2002-2010年曾任無綫新聞部港聞組、中國組高級記者，並曾被派駐北京和廣州，及後轉任專題記者，負責《星期日檔案》等新聞特輯節目的編輯和採訪工作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">離開新聞界\t</span><br />\n2010年尾，柳俊江於其博客透露已離開TVB和從事八年的新聞行業，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">表示近年「記者淪為『車衣女工』，新聞部管理層對每日的新聞早已有一套『看法』，記者很多時被要求『照單執藥』」</span></span>，文章流露他對新聞編輯自由以及記者的待遇抱有懷疑，因而求退。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc3414a1cb901278481c29b40fe35f90914f020","tid":1344739,"uid":271444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝早日康復"},{"pid":"46a2e8ec16262b268c231c81cd79477ec494cc58","tid":1344739,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共最叻以群眾鬥群眾，內耗消耗民意，<br />\n引起眾多火頭，燃起多條戰綫，力圖模糊最初目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"51e191c4fb3ca5387f3d19195d0564df2fbe963d","tid":1344739,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:35:44.000Z","msg":"事實證明離開TVB根本唔怕生存唔到<br />\n而家嗰啲PK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe007ac1433d2aa27db0b4a9d9b3f4991e726e8","tid":1344739,"uid":274756,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:37:51.000Z","msg":"雨傘果時已有留意佢<br />\n<br />\n佢個女出世時佢仲堅持留守，仲將個女改名叫Bella (Umbrella Revolution)"},{"pid":"0ca65c4b258f076dc607845648ffc7c2d8e1a